20out%20a%20high-quality%20olive%20oil%20is%20difficult%20for%20a%20young%20brand%2C%20but%20it's%20even%20harder%20now%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folive-oil-prices-surge-mediterranean-drought-food-inflation-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprices%20hit%20record%20highs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20launched%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGraza%20in%20early%202022%2C%20we%20purchased%20nearly%2050%2C000%20liters%20of%20olive%20oil%20from%20Italy%20for%20about%20%243.10%20a%20kilo.%20Fast%20forward%20to%20this%20month%20%E2%80%94%20when%20we%20made%20our%20most%20recent%20purchase%20%E2%80%94%20prices%20had%20shot%20up%20to%20%249.30%20a%20kilo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlive%20oil%20prices%20have%20jumped%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20due%20to%20extreme%20environmental%20conditions%20in%20the%20world's%20top%20olive%20oil-producing%20regions%20%E2%80%94%20Spain%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20Greece.%20Prolonged%20droughts%20and%20deficiencies%20in%20irrigated%20land%20have%20led%20to%20agricultural%20disruptions%20that%20have%20hampered%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20though%2C%20we've%20only%20passed%20on%20costs%20to%20retailers%20to%20increase%20the%20on-shelf%20price%20of%20%26quot%3BSizzle%2C%26quot%3B%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fcomparing-popular-olive-oil-brands%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextra%20virgin%20olive%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20for%20cooking%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BDrizzle%2C%26quot%3B%20our%20finishing%20oil%2C%20by%20about%20%241%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20trying%20not%20to%20pass%20on%20more%20costs%20because%20when%20you're%20a%20fast-growing%20brand%20like%20Graza%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20you%20want%20to%20do%20is%20paralyze%20demand%20by%20pricing%20yourself%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20didn't%20want%20to%20call%20attention%20to%20the%20adultery%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we%20have%20to.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20competition%20among%20suppliers%20to%20keep%20costs%20down%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20suppliers%20have%20resorted%20to%20compromising%20on%20quality%20to%20maintain%20their%20margins.%20If%20you%20know%20a%20bit%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl4GrYUUcQG0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eolive%20oil%20production%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20you'll%20know%20that%20extra%20virgin%20olive%20oil%20is%20extremely%20inefficient%20to%20produce%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20it's%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELampante%2C%20raw%20olive%20oil%20not%20intended%20for%20human%20consumption%2C%20is%20about%20%248.2%20per%20kilo.%20Virgin%20is%20%248.70%20per%20kilo.%20And%20extra%20virgin%20is%20%249.30%20per%20kilo.%20There%20are%20some%20big-time%20suppliers%20right%20now%20that%20are%20creating%20extra%20virgin%20products%20with%20oils%20that%20are%20not%20extra%20virgin%20because%20they're%20desperate%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20there's%20no%20biochemical%20marker%20for%20customers%20to%20know%20that%20the%20olive%20oil%20has%20been%20adulterated.%20And%20while%20Graza's%20platform%20wasn't%20intended%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-olive-oil-2012-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadultery%20in%20the%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20that%20we're%20seeing%20it%20with%20our%20own%20eyes%2C%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20call%20attention%20to%20it.%20Law%20enforcement%20agencies%20have%20seized%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20gallons%20of%20olive%20oil%20and%20arrested%20suspects%20worldwide%20for%20fraud%20in%20the%20past%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKeeping%20costs%20down%20right%20now%20is%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20we've%20ever%20faced%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20change%20our%20operations%20and%20make%20some%20tough%20decisions%20to%20continue%20delivering%20high-quality%20EVOO%20to%20our%20customers%20without%20increasing%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20implemented%20a%20hiring%20freeze.%20We're%20spending%20just%205%25%20of%20our%20gross%20revenue%20on%20marketing%2C%20down%20from%20around%2012.5%25.%20We're%20keeping%20our%20budget%20tight%2C%20not%20taking%20risks%2C%20and%20thinking%20long-term.%20Still%2C%20to%20have%20enough%20inventory%20of%20Drizzle%2C%20our%20finishing%20oil%2C%20to%20sell%20all%20year%20round%2C%20we%20must%20buy%20100%25%20of%20the%20supplies%20outright.%20Then%20we%20may%20go%20for%20months%20without%20returns%20on%20that%20investment.%20So%2C%20not%20passing%20the%20cost%20on%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20we%20have%20ever%20faced%20at%20Graza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20in%2010%2C000%20retail%20stores%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-and-target-are-looking-increasingly-similar-these-days-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20Walmart%20and%20Target%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20it's%20as%20easy%20as%20a%20snap%20of%20the%20finger%20to%20capitalize%20on%20our%20brand%20equity.%C2%A0But%20we're%20not%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20maintaining%20quality%20by%20putting%20our%20money%20where%20our%20mouth%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraza-olive-oil-cofounder-high-prices-inflation-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708863301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d133e96fcb546d2d511c42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraza-olive-oil-cofounder-high-prices-inflation-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Benin%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Graza%2C%20talks%20about%20how%20the%20startup%20is%20dealing%20with%20record-high%20olive%20oil%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Var