low.%20Stop%20me%20if%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Patil%2C%20who%20hit%20headlines%20for%20his%20hunger%20strike%20in%20demand%20of%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20last%20week%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20provide%20quota%20benefits%20to%20the%20politically-influential%20community%20that%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20new%20law%20is%20not%20in%20line%20with%20their%20demand.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20reservation%20which%20we%20deserve%2C%20give%20reservation%20under%20OBC%20category%20to%20those%20whose%20proof%20of%20being%20Kunbi%20has%20been%20found.%20For%20those%20who%20don't%20have%20proof%2C%20pass%20a%20law%20of%20'Sage%20Soyare'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patil%20said%20after%20the%20Bill%20cleared%20the%20Assembly.%20The%20quota%20agitation%20leader%20is%20demanding%20benefits%20for%20blood%20relations%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Kunbi%20sub-caste%20among%20Marathas.%20The%20Kunbis%20enjoy%20reservation%20within%20the%20OBC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20agitation%2C%20Mr%20Patil%20had%20demanded%20that%20all%20members%20of%20Maratha%20community%20be%20considered%20Kunbi%20and%20given%20reservations%20under%20the%20OBC%20Quota%2C%20but%20the%20state%20government%20decided%20that%20only%20people%20with%20Nizam-era%20Kunbi%20certificates%20will%20get%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFadnavis%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20rift%20within%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20Attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20finish%20big%20communities%20and%20give%20more%20prominence%20to%20smaller%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20said%20he%20is%20not%20affiliated%20to%20any%20political%20party.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20farmer's%20son.%20I%20will%20not%20spare%20Fadnavis.%20Attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20Maratha%20community%20and%20defame%20me.%20Fadnavis%20will%20be%20wiped%20off.%20I%20will%20ensure%20that%20relatives%20(of%20Marathas)%20get%20quota%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20brought%20by%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20is%20the%20third%20attempt%20in%20a%20decade%20to%20provide%20reservation%20benefits%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20The%20earlier%20two%20attempts%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20Congress's%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20and%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20were%20struck%20down%20by%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20factor%20behind%20the%20setbacks%20to%20the%20earlier%20laws%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20took%20the%20quantum%20of%20total%20reservation%20past%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20ceiling%20fixed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20warned%20that%20the%20legislation%20may%20not%20eventually%20clear%20the%20judicial%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20said%20it%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20brought%20by%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20fresh%20bill%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%20State%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20has%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20for%20bringing%20the%20law%20just%20before%20the%20elections.%20%26quot%3BThese%20types%20of%20laws%20were%20brought%20two%20times%2C%20but%20they%20were%20scrapped%20and%20put%20in%20a%20bin%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%202019%2C%20they%20did%20for%20the%20winning%20elections%20and%20now%20also%20they%20did%20for%20the%20elections.%20They%20want%20to%20take%20the%20credit%20for%20this.%20This%20will%20not%20work%20because%20it%20is%20done%20only%20for%20the%20election%20to%20get%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20has%20welcomed%20the%20legislation%20but%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20can%20be%20said%26quot%3B%20till%20it%20is%20implemented.%20Taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20his%20estranged%20lieutenant%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20the%20history%20of%20CM%20(Shinde).%20Therefore%2C%20till%20the%20time%20whatever%20he%20has%20said%20is%20implemented%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708859340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fvtf77ti8_manoj-jarange-patil_625x300_25_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-manoj-jarange-patil-d-fadnavis-trying-to-divide-marathas-quota-agitation-leader-hits-out-5124664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20Maratha%20quota%20agitation%20leader%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20today%20accused%20the%20BJP%20leader%20of%20hatching%20a%20plot%20to%20deny%20quota%20benefits%20to%20members%20of%20the%20community%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-manoj-jarange-patil-d-fadnavis-trying-to-divide-marathas-quota-agitation-leader-hits-out-5124664%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kumar%20Shahani%2C%20Pioneer%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Parallel%20Cinema%20Movement%2C%20Dies%20at%2083%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708859202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKumar-Shahani.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235921948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kumar%20Shahani%2C%20one%20of%20the%20pioneers%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20arthouse%20parallel%20cinema%20movement%2C%20died%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Feb.%2024%20after%20a%20period%20of%20illness.%20He%20w