0even%20to%20improve%20placement%20opportunities%20for%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20IIT%20Delhi%20director%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20clarification%20on%20BITS%20Pilani%20Dean%20to%20our%20alumni%20seeking%20help%20for%20Placements.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20email%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbitspilaniindia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40bitspilaniindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20Dean%20(Alumni)%20seeking%20help%20from%20alumni%20for%20placements%20is%20being%20blown%20out%20of%20proportions.%20It%20should%20be%20a%20very%20normal%20thing%20for%20institutions%20such%20as%20BITS%20and%20IITs%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkRcjv8iVFZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkRcjv8iVFZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20V.%20Ramgopal%20Rao%2C%20Ph.D.%20(%40ramgopal_rao)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framgopal_rao%2Fstatus%2F1761602190152720428%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20came%20as%20a%20clarification%20on%20%26quot%3BBITS%20Pilani%20Dean%20to%20our%20alumni%20seeking%20help%20for%20placements%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBITS%20Pilani's%20Arya%20Kumar%2C%20who%20is%20the%20current%20dean%20of%20alumni%20relations%2C%20sent%20out%20a%20notice%20to%20their%20alumni%20network%20for%20the%20second%20session%20of%20the%20placement%20season%2C%20Indian%20Express%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20well-aware%20of%20the%20current%20industry%20downturn%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20the%20businesses%20and%20prospective%20hiring.%20The%20global%20economy%20has%20not%20experienced%20this%20kind%20of%20slump%20for%20decades.%20The%20technology%20sector%20is%20radically%20impacted%2C%20with%20around%204%20lakh%20employees%20being%20laid%20off%20globally%20since%20January%202022.%20This%20uncertainty%20has%20a%20cascading%20effect%20with%20a%20funding%20winter%20setting%20in%2C%20resulting%20in%20cost-cutting%20in%20small%20and%20large%20businesses%20alike%2C%20with%20hiring%20being%20affected%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20including%20the%20campus%20level.%20In%20spite%20of%20business%20adversities%2C%20BITS%20Pilani%20has%20stood%20strong%2C%20with%20our%20closing%20placement%20statistics%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202022-23%20standing%20at%20a%20healthy%2089.2%25%20for%20Indian%20Campuses.%20Since%20then%2C%20however%2C%20the%20hiring%20slowdown%20has%20only%20deepened.%20Although%20the%20placement%20teams%20are%20doing%20their%20best%2C%20they%20would%20be%20very%20appreciative%20of%20support%20from%20our%20esteemed%20alumni%20to%20help%20them%20tide%20through%20the%20current%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EV%20Ramgopal%20Rao%20said%20that%20BITS%20Pilani%20has%20over%207400%20alumni%20in%20CEO%20and%20other%20senior%20positions%20in%20corporates%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BThis%20mail%20from%20our%20Dean%20elicited%20a%20very%20positive%20response%20from%20alumni%20and%20many%20have%20connected%20with%20us.%20We%20also%20conducted%20a%20startup%20week%20during%20Jan%2022-26%2C%202024%C2%A0%20in%20BITS%20for%20encouraging%20good%2C%20well-funded%20startups%20to%20hire%20our%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20students%20%26quot%3Breceived%20very%20attractive%20offers%26quot%3B%20from%20these%20startups.%20%26quot%3B24%20startups%20that%20met%20our%20screening%20criteria%20participated%20in%20it.%20Students%20received%20very%20attractive%20offers%20from%20them.%20BITS%20has%20over%206300%20startup%20founders%2Fco-founders%20among%20its%20ranks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedian%20salaries%20in%20BITS%20campuses%20range%20over%20Rs%2020%20lakhs%20for%20a%20batch%20size%20of%20roughly%203400%2C%20which%20is%20phenomenal%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20also%20asserted%20that%20if%20an%20institution%20is%20not%20tapping%20its%20eminent%20alumni%20network%20for%20placements%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20are%20doing%20something%20wrong%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirla%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%26amp%3B%20Science%20(BITS)%2C%20Pilani%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20six%20institutes%20in%20India%20to%20be%20granted%20Institute%20of%20Eminence%20status.%20It%20focuses%20primarily%20on%20higher%20education%20and%20research%20in%20engineering%20and%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708858920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fksdean74_bits-pilani_625x300_25_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbits-pilani-vice-chancellor-on-seeking-alumni-help-for-jobs-very-normal-thing-5124638%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20reports%20of%20the%20BITS%2C%20Pilani%20reaching%20out%20to%20their%20alumni%20network%20seeking%20help%20for%20placement%20process%20made%20headlines%2C%20its%20group%20vice-chancellor%20V%20Ramgopal%20Rao%20has%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20blown%20out%20of%20proportions%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbits-pilani-vice-chancellor-on-seeking-alumni-help-for-jobs-very-normal-thing-5124638%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Buffett%20calls%20late%20Charlie%20Munger%20'architect'%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708858801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107985703%2Cimgsize-1131090.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Fwarren-buffett-writes-letter-to-shareholders-credits-partner-charlie-munger-as-architect-of-business%2Farticleshow%2F107985667.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20annual%20letter%20to%20shareholders%2C%20Warren%2