%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20booming%2C%20frail%20voice.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20easy%20path%20to%20liberty%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20once%20you%20find%20it%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20at%20it.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFreedom%20of%20speech%2C%20but%20also%20freedom%20after%20speech.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20green%2C%20he%20once%20said%20to%20me%2C%20twenty-five%20summers%20young%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20full%20of%20heart.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDo%20not%20lose%20heart%2C%20he%20said%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20ocean%20is%20turbulent%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDo%20not%20lose%20faith.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBlessed%20with%20principle%2C%20but%20also%20someone%20who%20knew%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20to%20laugh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20enjoyed%20a%20joke%20like%20no%20tomorrow.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOld%20lawyers%20don%E2%80%99t%20fade%20away%2C%20he%20said%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20just%20lose%20their%20appeal.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20understood%2C%20how%20things%20pass%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20time%20makes%20way%20for%20no%20one%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%20page%20had%20to%20be%20written%2C%20and%20that%20argument%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20to%20be%20chiseled%20to%20perfection.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20liked%20the%20pen%20and%20signed%20his%20letters%2C%20to%20old%20and%20young%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESimply%20Fali.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmlanjyoti%20Goswami%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3ERiver%20Wedding%20(2019)%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3EVital%20Signs%20(2022)%3Cem%3E%2C%20published%20by%20Poetrywala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708855241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25144137%2F