e%20also%20made%20it%20well-nigh%20impossible%20for%20ordinary%20citizens%20to%20visit%20the%20Shambhu%20toll%20plaza%20and%20express%20solidarity%20with%20their%20%3Cem%3Eannadatas%3C%2Fem%3E%20camped%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20approaching%20Shambhu%20border%20from%20Haryana%20will%20find%20approach%20roads%20blocked%20and%20guarded%20by%20the%20police.%20They%20will%20also%20likely%20find%20Google%20Maps%20not%20working%20as%20internet%20access%20has%20been%20restricted%20across%20huge%20swathes%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20nearly%2050-km%20detour%20through%20rural%20Punjab%2C%20my%20taxi%20driver%20managed%20to%20get%20us%20to%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20the%20caravan%20of%20tractors%2C%20trolleys%20and%20tents%20stretching%20for%2010%20km%20from%20the%20Shambhu%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20farmers%20sitting%20on%20a%20mattress%20beneath%20the%20shade%20of%20their%20tractor%20brought%20back%20to%20memory%20the%20very%20first%20group%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20I%20ever%20met%2C%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Ghazipur%20border%20on%20a%20cold%2C%20smoggy%20December%20evening%20in%202020.%20They%20too%20had%20been%20sitting%20on%20a%20mattress%20by%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Meerut%20Express%20Highway.%20I%20still%20remember%20the%20very%20first%20question%20those%20Sikh%20farmers%20had%20asked%20me%20as%20I%20had%20approached%20them.%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20had%20something%20to%20eat%3F%E2%80%9D%20Certainly%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20question%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20this%20current%20group%20of%20farmers%20to%20explain%20their%20protest%20in%20terms%20simple%20enough%20for%20a%20non-farmer%20to%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%