mers%20have%20been%20instructed%20not%20to%20go%20beyond%20that%20rope.%20Strewn%20all%20over%20the%20road%20were%20gunny%20sacks%20which%20the%20farmers%20had%20thrown%20on%20exploding%20tear%20gas%20canisters%20to%20try%20and%20contain%20the%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20300%20metres%20from%20the%20border%2C%20a%20group%20called%20the%20United%20Sikhs%20had%20set%20up%20a%20medical%20camp%20for%20those%20injured%20in%20the%20recent%20tear%20gas%20shelling.%20They%20showed%20me%20huge%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20exploded%20tear%20gas%20cannisters%20and%20told%20me%20that%20military%20grade%20weapons%20were%20used%20on%20the%20farmers.%20They%20also%20told%20me%20that%20a%20tear%20gas%20cannister%20fired%20from%20a%20drone%20exploded%20right%20next%20to%20their%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CElderly%20people%20have%20inhaled%20tear%20gas%2C%20and%20it%20has%20damaged%20their%20lungs.%20We%20have%20removed%20pellets%20from%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20injured.%20Please%20go%20to%20Rajpura%20hospital%20and%20see%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20injured%20for%20yourself.%20What%20has%20happened%20here%20is%20very%2C%20very%20wrong!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20short%20distance%20away%2C%20Dr%20Harpreet%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20Ravinder%20Singh%2C%20two%20young%20doctors%20from%20Hoshiarpur%20were%20distributing%20medicines%20from%20the%20boot%20of%20their%20car.%20Mentioning%20their%20proximity%20to%20%E2%80%98ground%20zero%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20asked%20if%20they%20were%20afraid%20of%20getting%20injured%20in%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Harpreet%20smiled%2C%20shook%20his%20head%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20came%20here%2C%20%3Cem%3Esar%20pe%20kafan%20bandh%20ke%20aye%20thhe.%3C%2Fem%3E%20We%20came%20with%20the%20full%20awareness%20that%20we%20too%20could%20get%20injured%20or%20killed.%20But%20we%20are%20not%20afraid.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20fight%20for%20our%20rights.%20Our%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20Ji%20Maharaj%20has%20taught%20us%20that%20just%20as%20it%20is%20a%20sin%20to%20commit%20wrongdoing%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20sin%20to%20tolerate%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20shook%20their%20hands%20and%20told%20them%20I%20admired%20their%20courage%20and%20selflessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManinder%20Singh%2C%20a%20homemaker%2C%20told%20me%20she%20comes%20every%20morning%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Eseva%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20serve%20%3Cem%3Elangar%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20protestors%2C%20and%20then%20goes%20back%20home%20in%20the%20evening.%20She%20also%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20Guru%20Nanak%20Dev%20ji%20has%20not%20made%20us%20cowards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhvir%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Sri%20Muktsar%20Sahib%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGive%20us%20MSP%20for%20all%2023%20crops%20and%20we%20will%20diversify%20our%20crop%20cultivation%20and%20grow%20the%20crops%20that%20will%20neither%20deplete%20the%20water%20table%20nor%20compel%20us%20to%20burn%20%3Cem%3Eparali%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stubble)%20and%20pollute%20the%20air.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20fighting%20for%20ourselves%2C%20we%20are%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%20all%20over%20India.%20Farmers%20in%20Bihar%20are%20selling%20their%20rice%20for%20Rs%201%2C300%20a%20quintal%20whereas%20MSP%20for%20rice%20is%20Rs%202%2C200.%20We%20care%20about%20them%20too.%20Give%20us%20MSP%20based%20on%20Dr%20%5BM.S.%5D%20Swaminathan%E2%80%99s%20C2%2B50%25%20formula%20and%20we%20will%20go%20home.%20We%20aren%E2%80%99t%20mad%20to%20want%20to%20sit%20here%20on%20the%20road%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3-1024x577.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20farmer%20at%20Shambhu%20border.%20Photo%3A%20Rohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20did%20not%20conceal%20their%20pain%20at%20being%20attacked%20by%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%20own%20sons%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20barricading%E2%80%9D.%20While%20the%20quiet%20tenacity%20and%20courage%20of%20the%20farmers%20continues%20to%20be%20inspiring%2C%20it%20is%20deeply%20alarming%20is%20to%20see%20the%20massive%20deficit%20of%20trust%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20heavy-handedness%20and%20lack%20of%20empathy%20has%20created%20not%20just%20between%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekisan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Esarkaar%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20also%20between%20the%3Cem%3E%20kisan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejawaan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20elderly%20farmer%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20perhaps%20expressed%20the%20tragedy%20of%20the%20situation%20best%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20forgive%20those%20who%20have%20hurt%20us%2C%20for%20they%20were%20acting%20under%20orders%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20feed%20you%20for%20that%20is%20what%20we%20do%2C%20but%20we%20will%20never%2C%20ever%20forget%20the%20%3Cem%3Evishvaasghaat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(betrayal)%20that%20has%20been%20has%20done%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERohit%20Kumar%20is%20an%20educator%2C%20author%2C%20and%20independent%20journalist%2C%20and%20can%20be%20reached%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aletsempathize%40gmail.com%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eletsempathize%40gmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22