B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Continue%20To%20Remain%20CEO%26quot%3B%3A%20Byju%20Raveendran%20Day%20After%20Shareholders'%20Move%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20growing%20trouble%20in%20the%20edtech%20firm%20Byju's%2C%20company's%20CEO%20Byju%20Raveendran%20told%20employees%20that%20he%20continues%20to%20remain%20the%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20the%20company.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbyju-raveendran-says-reports-of-expulsion-exaggerated-and-highly-inaccurate%5C%22%3EMr%20Raveendran%20wrote%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20employees%20denying%20media%20reports%20of%20him%20being%20ousted%20as%20the%20company's%20CEO%20and%20called%20the%20media%20reports%20%E2%80%9Cgreatly%20exaggerated%20and%20highly%20inaccurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbiz-byjus-letter%5C%22%3EThe%20letter%20read%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20our%20company.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20you%20may%20have%20read%20in%20the%20media%2C%20I%20continue%20to%20remain%20CEO%2C%20the%20management%20remains%20unchanged%2C%20and%20the%20board%20remains%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbusiness%20as%20usual%E2%80%9D%20at%20BYJU'S%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20reemphasise%2C%20the%20rumours%20of%20my%20firing%20have%20been%20greatly%20exaggerated%20and%20highly%20inaccurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20just%20a%20day%20after%20shareholders%20(prominent%20investors)%20on%20Friday%20voted%20%E2%80%9Cunanimously%E2%80%9D%20to%20unseat%20Mr%20Raveendran%20from%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20this%20vote%2C%20Mr%20Raveendran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20you%20can't%20change%20the%20rules%20of%20a%20game%20midway%20without%20agreement%20from%20all%20players%2C%20we%20can't%20alter%20how%20our%20company%20is%20run%20without%20fo