%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTq0kWs1q3hI%5C%22%3Ewarn%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpwccc.wordpress.com%2Fsupport%2F%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20was%20it%20that%20prompted%20such%20a%20dramatic%20change%20in%20the%20way%20so%20many%20people%20chose%20to%20live%2C%20to%20shift%20from%20immediate-return%20to%20delayed-return%20economies%3F%20From%20socially%20egalitarian%2C%20decentralized%2C%20diverse%20and%20fluidly%20inter-linked%20communities%20to%20deeply%20stratified%2C%20centralized%2C%20relatively%20homogeneous%20and%20bounded%20nation-states%3F%20When%20did%20it%20all%20begin%20to%20change%3F%20Why%3F%20And%20as%20a%20species%2C%20why%20are%20we%20not%20(yet)%20suffering%20population%20decline%20when%20we%20so%20utterly%20despoil%20our%20environment%2C%20as%20our%20ancestors%20suffered%20if%20they%20ruined%20theirs%3F%20The%20answers%20may%20not%20be%20what%20most%20of%20us%20are%20led%20to%20presume.%20I%20will%20attempt%20to%20tease%20them%20out%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20essays%20of%20this%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUsha%20Alexander%20trained%20in%20science%20and%20anthropology.%20After%20working%20for%20years%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20now%20lives%20in%20Gurugram.%20She%E2%80%99s%20written%20two%20novels%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Legend%20of%20Virinara%3Cem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EOnly%20the%20Eyes%20Are%20Mine%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708843504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25113632%2FIMG_2939.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Energy%20and%20materials%20flow%20through%20this%20circle%20of%20life%E2%80%94really%2C%20multiple%20interconnected%20circles%2C%20or%20a%20web%20of%20life%E2%80%94with%20each%20species%2