0Friendship%20Dam%2C%20was%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20a%20global%20effort%20aimed%20at%20reconstructing%20Afghanistan%20and%20staving%20off%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20country%20having%20fallen%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Taliban%2C%20India%20had%20the%20choice%20of%20leaving%20it%20to%20the%20militant%20group%20or%20helping%20to%20maintain%20it.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20chosen%20the%20latter%2C%20sending%20a%20four-member%20team%20to%20the%20hydropower%20project%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20engagement%20with%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learned%20that%20a%20four-member%20team%20from%20the%20Indian%20public%20sector%20company%20Wapcos%20is%20currently%20visiting%20Salma%20Dam%2C%20their%20hydroelectric%20project%20built%20on%20the%20Harirud%20River%20in%20a%20remote%20part%20of%20north-western%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20journeyed%20to%20Kabul%20via%20the%20weekly%20scheduled%20flight%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20proceeding%20to%20Herat%20city%20next%20day.%20They%20took%20a%20helicopter%20ride%20to%20the%20dam%20site%2C%20where%20they%20stayed%20for%20three%20days%20before%20embarking%20on%20their%20return%20trip.%20Local%20security%20officials%20and%20representatives%20from%20the%20Afghan%20Ministry%20of%20Energy%20and%20Water%20accompanied%20them%20throughout%20their%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weathered%20name%20board%20at%20the%20dam%20site%20mirrored%20the%20evolving%20political%20landscape%20in%20Afghanistan.%20Set%20against%20a%20blue%20backdrop%2C%20the%20inscription%20%E2%80%9CAfghan%20India%20Friendship%20Dam%E2%80%9D%20remained%20prominently%20displayed%2C%20while%20several%20other%20lines%20had%20gradually%20faded.%20On%20top%2C%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20Indian%20flag%20remained%20vibrant%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20symbol%20of%20entwined%20hands.%20But%20the%20tricolour%20flag%20of%20the%20Afghan%20republic%2