-Image-2024-02-24-at-23.09.55-461x1024.jpeg%20461w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698741%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22867%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20latest%20view%20from%20top%20of%20the%20dam%20towards%20the%20power%20house%20and%20the%20river.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20appointed%20state-run%20Wapcos%20to%20execute%20the%20project%2C%20the%20state%20firm%20contracted%20the%20construction%20to%20a%20joint%20venture%20of%20two%20private%20firms%2C%20SSJV%20and%20Angelique%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInaugurated%20jointly%20by%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20then%20Afghan%20President%20Ashraf%20Ghani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2Fprintrelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D145967%5C%22%3Ein%20June%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20the%20first%20major%20water%20infrastructure%20project%20in%20modern%20Afghanistan%20in%20the%20last%2050%20years.%20The%20project%20was%20also%20diplomatically%20sensitive%20as%20Iran%20had%20objected%20to%20its%20construction%20over%20concerns%20that%20water%20flow%20in%20the%20river%20that%20crossed%20over%20into%20Iranian%20territory%20would%20reduce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20decade%2C%20amidst%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20precarious%20security%20conditions%20and%20logistical%20intricacies%2C%20the%20project%20endured%2C%20demanding%20a%20ballooning%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%201775.69%20crore%20(%24265%20million%20in%202016%20exchange%20rate)%20to%20reach%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELinked%20to%20Herat%20city%20by%20a%20165-kilometre%20earthen%20road%2C%20traversable%20only%20under%20escort%20of%20a%20large%20convoy%20of%20security%20personnel%2C%20the%20journey%20consumed%20seven%20to%20eight%20arduous%20hours.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20security%20landscape%20progressively%20deteriorated%20in%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20final%20years%2C%20all%20ground%20travel%20was%20abruptly%20barred%2C%20compelling%20Indian%20workers%20at%20the%20site%20to%20rely%20solely%20on%20helicopters%20for%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20commissioning%2C%20the%20dam%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Afghan%20engineers%20and%20technicians%20who%20had%20been%20trained%20in%20India.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20teams%20from%20Wapcos%20made%20occasional%20visits%20to%20the%20dam%20for%20inspections%20to%20address%20initial%20operational%20challenges.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20India%2C%20the%20main%20contractor%20sued%20Wapcos%20for%20non-payment%20of%20dues%20of%20over%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20in%20a%20case%20that%20has%20to%20be%20still%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Taliban%20started%20to%20relentlessly%20press%20their%20military%20blitzkrieg%20in%202021%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khaama.com%2Ftaliban-kill-16-security-personnel-near-salma-dam%2F%5C%22%3Efighting%20became%20increasingly%20closer%20to%20the%20site%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20July%202021%2C%20Taliban%20entered%20Chisti%20Sharif%2C%20the%20nearest%20town%20to%20the%20dam%2C%20and%20damaged%20the%20complex%20of%20rooms%20that%20Wapcos%20had%20built%20for%20staff%20during%20the%20construction%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDevirupaM%2Fstatus%2F1426127389197692932%5C%22%3EOn%20August%2013%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20local%20Taliban%20commander%20entered%20the%20dam%20complex%20after%20the%20soldiers%20surrendered%20following%20the%20Friday%20prayers.%20Soon%2C%20the%20white%20and%20black%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdevirupam%2Fstatus%2F1427243280652283909%5C%22%3ETaliban%20flag%20fluttered%20over%20the%20dam%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%2C%20President%20Ghani%20and%20his%20aides%20fled%20to%20Uzbekistan%2C%20allowing%20the%20Taliban%20to%20seize%20control%20of%20Kabul%20and%20the%20entire%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexclusive-surrounded-by-taliban-india-built-salma-dams-future-is-uncertain%5C%22%3ESurrounded%20by%20Taliban%2C%20India-Built%20Salma%20Dam%E2%80%99s%20Future%20is%20Uncertain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20many%20of%20the%20Afghan%20engineers%20had%20migrated%20abroad%20in%20those%20uncertain%20days%2C%20the%20challenge%20in%20the%20new%20Taliban%20era%20was%20to%20find%20trained%20manpower%20to%20operate%20the%20hydropower%20project.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20attrition%20had%20begun%20months%20prior%20to%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20assumption%20of%20power%2C%20as%20salary%20payments%20dwindled%20owing%20to%20the%20Afghan%20government%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698739%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%202022%20photo%20showing%20the%20damaged%20Wapcos%20accommodation%20in%20Chisti%20Sharif.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technical%20team%20from%20Wapcos%20has%20gone%20with%20a%20list%20of%20items%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20assessed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20SCADA%20system%2C%20which%