tabilising%20role%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20lifesaving%20humanitarian%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependent%20review%20group%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20appointed%20an%20independent%20review%20group%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146207%5C%22%3Eearly%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20Israeli%20allegations%20that%2012%20UNRWA%20employees%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20Hamas-led%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20led%20by%20former%20French%20minister%C2%A0Catherine%20Colonna%20aims%20to%20meet%20Palestinian%20officials%20and%20may%20request%20a%20visit%20to%20Gaza.%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20is%20to%20deliver%20a%20report%20that%20is%20rigorous%20and%20evidence%20based%E2%80%A6and%20to%20do%20our%20best%20so%20we%20can%20help%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%20deliver%20under%20the%20mandate%20given%20%5Bto%20it%5D%20by%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Colonna%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146857%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20began%20its%20work%20on%20February%2013%20and%20expects%20to%20have%20an%20interim%20report%20by%20late%20March.%20Further%2C%20Colonna%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Esaid%20the%20group%20intends%20to%20issue%20recommendations%20in%20its%20final%20report%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20on%20April%2020%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EUN%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemand%20for%20change%20in%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20funding%20structure%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELazzarini%20suggested%20that%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20faces%20a%20fundamental%20decision%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20either%20allow%20UNRWA%20to%