es%20that%20the%20fertiliser%20comprises%20helps%20plants%20thrive%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20climates%20and%20environments%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20the%20miracle%20product%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20his%20internship%20years%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(BHU)%20Varanasi%2C%20(IITBHU)%20that%20Akshay%E2%80%99s%20idea%20got%20scale.%20The%20technical%20internship%20in%202019%20introduced%20him%20to%20facets%20of%20integrating%20tech%20into%20business%20and%20commercialising%20an%20idea%20for%20social%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Akshay%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%E2%80%99s%20RKVY-RAFTAAR%20Scheme%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20of%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20allied%20sectors.%20While%20the%20idea%20of%20biofertilisers%20had%20taken%20root%20in%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20delved%20into%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20But%20whilst%20at%20IITBHU%2C%20he%20recalls%20a%20seminar%20that%20helped%20him%20with%20his%20eureka%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20the%20processes%20of%20developing%20biofuel%20and%20biofertiliser%20were%20very%20similar.%20Both%20involve%20agricultural%20biomass%20being%20treated%20with%20microbes.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%20began%20the%20journey%20of%20Akshay%20and%20his%20mentor%20testing%20different%20kinds%20of%20microbes%20across%20farming%20lands%20for%20their%20characteristics%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20see%20which%20would%20work%20best%20when%20added%20to%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%202020%2C%20Akshay%20had%20manage