-specific%20and%20rarely%20grown%20in%20the%20country.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-4-1708522473.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-4-1708522473-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-4-1708522473-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-4-1708522473-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-4-1708522473-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENagendra%20wanted%20to%20start%20growing%20a%20fruit%20that%20was%20region-specific%20and%20rarely%20grown%20in%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20degree%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursued%20an%20MBA%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20working%20in%20a%20startup.%20%E2%80%9CI%20later%20moved%20on%20to%20companies%20like%20Apple%2C%20Tracxn%2C%20and%20I-PAC%2C%20understanding%20how%20quality%20control%20and%20supply%20chain%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20acquired%20a%20failing%20company%20and%20turned%20it%20around%20into%20a%20profit-making%20one%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20was%20always%20thinking%20of%20how%20I%20could%20enter%20the%20agri%20space.%20I%20needed%20a%20solid%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20a%20good%20and%20niche%20product%2C%20the%20right%20labour%20and%20a%20strong%20supply%20chain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20enjoying%20his%20work%2C%20his%20true%20passion%20lay%20in%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CIt%2