0it%20was%20raining!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20did%20the%20family%20do%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wore%20our%20raincoats%20and%20continued%20driving%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Daman.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20knew%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20be%20sunshine%20and%20rainbows%20all%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20And%20so%20the%20family%20of%20seven%2C%20Daman%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20his%2075-year-old%20father%2C%20his%2021-year-old%20daughter%2C%20a%20photographer%20friend%2C%20and%20an%20uncle%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339529%2Fjaipur-neeru-saluja-senior-citizen-woman-travels-solo-to-eighty-countries-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrove%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20support%20vehicle%20behind%20that%20held%20the%20luggage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESuitcases%20of%20memories%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20theme%20of%20every%20day.%20But%20no%20one%20was%20complaining.%20Recalling%20a%20nerve-wracking%20episode%20they%20had%20when%20they%20crossed%20the%20Turkey%20border%2C%20Daman%20shares%20how%20they%20were%20set%20to%20reach%20their%20pre-booked%20stay%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20but%20reached%20at%203%3A30%20am.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20designated%20guy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20answering.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20manage%20to%20book%20any%20new%20place.%20So%2C%20we%20drove%20around%20in%20the%20car%20until%20we%20managed%20to%20find%20somewhere%20to%20stay!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20gamble%20with%20fate%20is%20what%20the%20trip%20was.%20%E2%80%9CThroughout%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335875%2Fgoa-stay-lawyer-panta-ferrao-built-khaama-kethna-eco-village-jungle-retreat-tree-house-cottage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22