App-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-1708430529.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iconic%20adventure%20was%20flagged%20off%20from%20Mumbai%20on%2015%20August%202023%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-1708430529.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-1708430529-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-1708430529-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-1708430529-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-1708430529-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342439%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20iconic%20adventure%20was%20flagged%20off%20from%20Mumbai%20on%2015%20August%202023.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHere%20I%20was%20with%20gadgets%2C%20Google%20Maps%2C%20a%20phone%2C%20technology%20and%20the%20latest%20roads.%20But%20this%20man%20had%20done%20it%20at%20a%20time%20when%20none%20of%20this%20existed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20love%20for%20India%20only%20became%20more%20evident%20as%20the%20group%20neared%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335137%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-life-after-retirement-trekking-riding-travelling-biking-road-trips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20destination%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Bulgaria%2C%20we%20stopped%20for%20engine%20oil%20at%20a%20small%20village%20which%20is%20home%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20orthodox%20churches%20in%20the%20world.%20A%20woman%20in%20her%20fifties%20asked%20us%20to%20accept%20the%20fuel%20for%20free.%20The%20fact%20that%20we%20were%20Indians%20got%20us%20this%20favour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20woman%20explained%2C%20her%20love%20for%20India%20had%20led%20her%20to%20memorise%20the%20Bhagwad%20Gita%20and%20the%20Ramayana.%20She%20was%20well-versed%20in%20Sanskrit%20and%20was%20a%20fan%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20surprised%20to%20know%20she%20had%20never%20been%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Daman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20has%20goodwill%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20kindness%20never%20left%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Daman%20recounts%20how%20a%20man%20named%20Anil%20helped%20him%20through%20a%20sticky%20spot.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20car%20had%20broken%20down%20and%20it%20was%20very%20expensive%20to%20hire%20a%20pickup%20truck%20there.%20I%20had%20visited%20Anil%20for%20a%20few%20car-related%20things%20the%20previous%20day%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20car%20broke%20down%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20could%20send%20someone%20to%20help.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20Anil%20drive%20600%20miles%20to%20help%20but%20did%20not%20charge%20a%20penny%20for%20it.%20%E2%80%9CYesterday%20when%20you%20drove%20Lal%20Pari%20to%20my%20garage%2C%20you%20brought%20a%20smile%20to%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20face.%20I%20cannot%20charge%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20excuse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%E2%80%99s%20more%20fascinating%20is%20the%20number%20of%20people%20Daman%20met%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334987%2Fmumbai-battling-rheumatoid-arthritis-parvinder-chawla-shares-tips-on-wheelchair-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20incredible%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20undertook%20%E2%80%93%20fifty%20thousand%20people%20and%20counting!%20And%20when%20he%20finally%20reached%20the%20destination%2C%20the%20exhilaration%20was%20visible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lal%20Pari%20encountered%20all%20sorts%20of%20weather%20on%20this%20adventurous%20voyage%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342440%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELal%20Pari%20encountered%20all%20sorts%20of%20weather%20on%20this%20adventurous%20voyage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-6-1708430653.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20support%20vehicle%20tagged%20behind%20Lal%20Pari%20the%20entire%20